        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Microsoft 遊戲部門裁員 1,900 人　前 Activision Blizzard 員工和 Xbox 團隊受影響</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/microsoft-lays-off-1900-activision-blizzard-xbox-staff/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-lays-off-1900-activision-blizzard-xbox-staff</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/microsoft-lays-off-1900-activision-blizzard-xbox-staff/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 15:00:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Activision Blizzard]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[microsoft]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[xbox]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1217598</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>經過一番波折，Microsoft 才終於成功完成收購 Activision Blizzard 不久，最近就宣佈針對遊戲部門裁員，影響約 8% 員工。<br /><span id="more-1217598"></span></p><p>Microsoft 最近發出內部備忘錄，表示在 Activision、Blizzard 和 King 團隊加入 Microsoft 之後，認為需要精簡重疊的架構進行重組，從而減省不必要的開支來專注於核心業務增長，在裁員計劃之下，遊戲部門包括原 Activision Blizzard 員工和 Xbox 團隊之中會有 1,900 人受影響。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">I want to thank everyone who is impacted today for their meaningful contributions to their teams, to Blizzard, and to players’ lives. It’s an incredibly hard day and my energy and support will be focused on all those amazing individuals impacted – this is in no way a reflection…</p><p>&mdash; Mike Ybarra 🎄 (@Qwik) <a href="https://twitter.com/Qwik/status/1750527310493868293?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 25, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>Activision Blizzard 前總裁 Mike Ybarra 早前已經宣佈收購過渡完成後將會離職，同時其前設計總監 Allen Adham 也會離職，顯示團隊加入 Microsoft 之後領導層也會有不少的變動，而除了人員變動外，本身 Activision Blizzard 正在開發的一個生存遊戲也會取消開發，將資源重新分配給其他項目。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-lays-off-1900-activision-blizzard-xbox-staff-verge-2024-01-25/">Reuters</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/02/activision-blizzard-android-app-store/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">曾考慮自設 Android 遊戲商店   Activision Blizzard 嫌賺錢不多放棄計劃</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/microsoft-lays-off-1900-activision-blizzard-xbox-staff/game-channel/">Microsoft 遊戲部門裁員 1,900 人　前 Activision Blizzard 員工和 Xbox 團隊受影響</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
